ANN MARIE KING TO APPEAR AT OLYMPIC GARDENS, LYNN, MA:
Come see comedian/singer Ann Marie King at the charming Olympic Gardens Restaurant, 41 Buffum St., Lynn, MA, tomorrow night from 6-7:30pm. You will laugh, have fun and enjoy the festive Greek atmosphere, with dinner cuisine par excellance!! Jazz Pianist Masako Fujimoto will accompany Ann Marie with relaxing jazz and peppy show tunes. See for yourself why Ann Marie's infectious personality and wit are gaining her increasing popularity throughout the Northeast! She is young and vibrant, and... NO COVER CHARGE!!! Great food and great entertainment, the place to be on Friday night! ~Recommended Highly by Al Nesser, TV Producer & CEO for The Harmony Hill Performing Arts Foundation (Two Thumbs Up!!)
